data.name: btn_choose_nmap.ToolTip
data.value: Normal map is necessary to create bump.

data.name: btn_choose_gloss.ToolTip
data.value: Gloss map is optional, if you don't have such it will be filled with default value.

data.name: btn_choose_height.ToolTip
data.value: Height map is optional, if you don't have such it will be filled with default value.

data.name: btn_dis_bump.ToolTip
data.value: Disassembles _bump and _bump# into height map, gloss map and normal map.

data.name: btn_create_bump.ToolTip
data.value: Compile all selected texture maps into _bump and _bump#

data.name: bump_text_box.ToolTip
data.value: Give your bump a name, for example: act_1. The result will be: act_1_bump and act_1_bump#. If you don't do it the result will be: image_bump and image_bump#.

data.name: force_lin_gloss.ToolTip
data.value: This flag forces gloss to be stored in linear rather than log.
